verse.lines:
I will triumph in the trials
I will glory in the cross;
I will stand upon the mountain,
Walk through the fire untouched;
Though the world may rise against me,
My strength is in the Lord;
I will be an overcomer
For He has overcome the world.

Problems maybe great
But my God is greater still;
So I'll walk out on this valley
And proclaim the Father's will;
And when it feels just like the end
He will open up the door;
I know that I shall overcome
And be much stronger than before.
